<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pet Care</title>

    <!--Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM"
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>

<body style="background-color: rgb(248, 239, 230);">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand ms-5" href="#" style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 25px;">Pet.care</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarText"
                aria-controls="navbarText" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>

            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarText" style="font-size: 18px; color: black;">
                <ul class="navbar-nav mx-auto mb-2 mb-lg-0 justify-content-center">
                    <li class="nav-item ms-5">
                        <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="">Home</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item ms-5">
                        <a class="nav-link active" href="/bookings_user">My Appointments</a>
                    </li>
                    <!-- <li class="nav-item ms-5">
                        <a class="nav-link active" href="#">Pricing</a>
                    </li> -->
                </ul>
                <span class="navbar-text">
                    <% if (currentUser) { %>
                        <span class="me-2" style="font-weight: bold;">Welcome, <%= currentUser.username %></span>
                        <a href="/logout" class="me-2"
                            style="border-radius: 25px; padding: 10px 20px; border: none; text-decoration: none; background-color: #573f1d73; color: black; font-weight: bold;">Logout</a>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <a href="/login" class="me-2"
                                style="border-radius: 25px; padding: 10px 20px; border: none; text-decoration: none; background-color: #573f1d73; color: black; font-weight: bold;">Login</a>
                            <% } %>
                                <a href="/register" class="me-2"
                                    style="border-radius: 25px; padding: 10px 20px; border: none; text-decoration: none; background-color: #573f1d73; color: black; font-weight: bold;">Sign up</a>
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <br>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="text ms-5">
            <h1>Care for your <br><strong>precious pets.</strong></h1>
            <p>We believe in treating your companions with the best care possible. <br> So we make sure every member
                of our family is happy and healthy.</p>
            <!-- <button style="border-radius: 25px; padding: 10px 20px; border: none;">Our Service</button> -->
            <a href="/booking"
                style="display: inline-block; border-radius: 25px; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #3a2405a0; color: white; text-decoration: none; border: none;">
                Book an Appointment</a>
        </div>
        <!-- <div class="hero-images">
      <img src="" alt="Cat">
      <img src="" alt="Kitten">
    </div> -->
    </section>
    <br>
    <section class="info-section"
        style="text-align: center; margin: 20px auto; display: block; border-radius: 100px; max-width: 1200px; padding: 100px; 
  background-color: #f0e5d775; color: rgb(2, 2, 2); text-decoration: none; border: none; box-shadow: 0 0 20px 5px rgba(184, 149, 101, 0.5);">
        <h1 style="font-weight: bold;">How we can help</h1>
        <br>
        <p>Vaccines</p>
        <p>Routine checkups</p>
        <p>Spaying</p>
        <p>Dental care</p>
        <!-- <img src="/images/puppy.png" alt="Puppy"> -->
    </section>
    <br>

    <section class="how-to-care">
        <!-- <img src="/images/cat3.png" alt="Cat"> -->
        <div style="padding-right: 50px; text-align: right;">
            <h2 style="font-weight: bold;">How to take care <br>â€” of your pets</h2>
            <p>Keeping your pets healthy is just as important as feeding them or giving them love.
                <br>Whether it's time for annual vaccines, a wellness check, or something more serious,
                finding the right vet is key.
                <br>After all, not every clinic is prepared to handle the unique needs of your furry family members.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <br>
    <footer>
        <div class="newsletter ms-5">
            <h3>Subscribe to our Newsletter</h3>
            <p>Receive Pet.care News and Promotions</p>
            <form action="/subscribe" method="POST">
                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your E-mail address">
                <button type="submit" style="border-radius: 25px; padding: 10px 20px; border: lightgrey;">
                    Subscribe Now</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </footer>
    <br></br>
</body>
</html>
